data.description: Located in the fabulous Silverado neighborhood whose amenities include, pool, park, and sport court areas, this adorable and tree nestled 4 bdrm/2.5 bath can be home to you! Located in a cul-de-sac, a roof replacement in 7/23, this home is seated on a large lot perfect for summer BBQ's. A must see is the large primary bathroom with a soaking garden tub and a double vanity. Only 15 minutes to South Austin and only a few minutes from tons of shopping and dining! This home is zoned to Kyle Elem., Wallace MS, and Hays High School. A true gem in West Kyle! Community pool and playgrounds. Minutes from all the essential shopping and the brand new COSTCO!
